[Chikungunya virus is endemic in India, so sporadic cases and
outbreaks are not surprising.

Maps showing the location of Ganjam district in Orissa state can be
accessed at http://healthmap.org/r/1cb7 and
http://www.mapsofindia.com/maps/orissa/orissa.htm. - Mod.TY]
